00:24:25,880 --> 00:24:31,080
♫ <i>Every failure is an ideal and vivid expression</i> ♫

366
00:24:31,080 --> 00:24:32,380
Xiaoju, fighting!

367
00:24:32,380 --> 00:24:38,200
♫ <i>Can you put it down? Can you just let it go like that?</i> ♫

368
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,430
Run! Run!

369
00:24:49,010 --> 00:24:51,500
Xiaoju, fighting!

370
00:25:00,280 --> 00:25:07,140
♫ <i>Strength is the sea living inside my heart</i> ♫

