00:25:19,190 --> 00:25:20,830
<i>Fighting!</i>

374
00:25:20,830 --> 00:25:28,160
♫ <i>Those cowardly people won't understand, just bravely go and explore your dreams</i> ♫

375
00:25:28,160 --> 00:25:30,280
Fighting!

